        Outside the classroom, Julian is deeply immersed in the creative arts. As an <strong>actor</strong> and musical <strong>artist</strong>, Jphood tells stories, performs music that resonates with youth, and brings his raw talent into every song and performance. He balances entertainment with a message, proving himself as more than just a student — but a full-blown creative force.
      </p>

